---
title: Pan-Fried Lemon Bream with Saffron and Chicken Rice
description: Well, this is something pretty special! Lemon-infused sea bream sits atop a generous portion of golden rice. Inspired by a Spanish paella, it's studded with juicy chicken pieces and scented with saffron. For a final flourish, everything gets finished off with a touch of parsley and lemon oil. Enjoy!
